/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c817b5497521491f3d893196f784919ec3193dd","tid":762602,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d9adf67105a404be454f5617f660599b2cf94d","tid":762602,"uid":47359,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"五毛沙田you<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/212958_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F212958_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bed79439&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c31dd6ae78f1b27d247fc28700ef0cd9d975109","tid":762602,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4df35ef7be3960ddf92be810353de37fa720bc","tid":762602,"uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"57d9adf67105a404be454f5617f660599b2cf94d","tid":762602,"uid":47359,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"五毛沙田you<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/212958_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F212958_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bed79439&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:39:09.000Z","msg":"五毛關你做實事搞港獨未？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/213906_ded8aeeef2d12b5e335f388680bcc04c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F213906_ded8aeeef2d12b5e335f388680bcc04c.png&h=6c03987f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cf55265ccf5db3e338f3ab6368d1db45422f072","tid":762602,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"520895f31bf9ecc8c58fe040b852533de6a211a3","tid":762602,"uid":51129,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"DIY武器新時代降臨：美國3D列印槍枝合法化<br />\n<br />\n美國槍械問題即將進入新時代，8月1日（周三）起，3D列印槍枝在美國合法化。9個州的檢察長聯手向聯邦法院提告，要求法院禁止特朗普政府開放3D列印槍枝。<br />\n<br />\n事緣一個名為Defense Distributed的組織創辦人Cody Wilson在2013年上載了3D列印槍枝解構圖，大受歡迎，其後美國國務院以違反出口規則為理由，要求Cody Wilson撤下有關內容。不過，據估計在解構圖撤銷前已錄得10萬次下載。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCody Wilson在2015年提出控訴，指政府的禁制令違反了美國憲法所保障的言論自由，也違反了人民擁有槍械的權益。今年6月，美國政府同Cody Wilson達成協議，並願意支付4萬美元的法律訴訟費用。在得到放行下，Cody Wilson宣布在8月1日再次上載3D列印槍枝的藍圖，並表示：「下載槍枝時代正式展開」。<br />\n<br />\n由於3D列印槍枝不需要序號，執法部門將無從追蹤，而所有被禁止擁有槍支的人，包括重犯、家庭施虐者，青少年以至有暴力傾向的精神病患者，都可以隨時自行製造槍支。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n包括加州、麻省、馬里蘭州在內的9個州連同哥倫比亞特區聯手，向西雅圖的華盛頓州西區美國聯邦地區法院（ U.S. District Court for the Western District of Washington）提告，要求法院發布禁制令，禁止Defense Distributed上載3D槍枝藍圖。<br />\n<br />\n另外，21名州檢察長致函司法部長傑夫&middot;塞申斯（Jeff Sessions）和國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo），指國務院的決定「極度危險，可能對公共安全產生前所未有的影響。」<br />\n<br />\n在賓夕法尼亞州，政府官員早前與Defense Distributed達成臨時協議，暫時禁止居民下載3D槍枝藍圖。賓夕法尼亞州總檢察長Josh Shapiro表示，在網上發布打印槍枝的操作手冊的想法令人髮指，整件事看來像個荒誕的笑話。政府要盡一切辦法阻止這種事發生，因為3D列印槍枝一旦實現，就不可能追回來。<br />\n<br />\n不過Cody Wilson表明會提出反對：「我不是擔心自己，而是為賓夕法尼亞州的人民感到憂慮，這對人民來說根本就是惡法（禁止上載藍圖）。老實說，令人有點難過。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紐約於周一宣布，所有3D列印槍枝的人都要取得槍枝製造商牌照，同時要登記槍枝。其他州亦趕緊研究緊急對策，務求在8月1日前暫時禁止Defense Distributed發布藍圖。<br />\n<br />\nCody Wilson在回應《紐約時報》查詢時說：「這些州政府官員利用自己的職權來威脅我的合法活動，含混地指稱那是違法，他們以為自己的權力可以凌駕美國憲法第一修正案（保障宗教、言論、新聞及集會自由），他們現在要關閉一個網站呀，這真過份。」<br />\n<br />\n據《紐約時報》報道，Defense Distributed於上星期起已逐步放出藍圖，到美國時間周一（30日）傍晚，3D打印的AR-15半自動步槍已被下載超過2500次，至於其他藍圖，其實早在網上流傳多年。由於打印槍支毋須序號，執法部門無法追蹤，故又被稱為「鬼槍」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:39:53.000Z","msg":"五毛群龍共舞<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/213948_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F213948_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=35c628b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/213949_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F213949_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ddd1b814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/213951_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F213951_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5190a0f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40c641f6a99b6ffef7b0b2f323d374318523248f","tid":762602,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T14:00:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6974998f27c7c5eafc8ce146f94f0d3c11b4eeda","tid":762602,"uid":2748,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T14:22:03.000Z","msg":"呢D偽獨派吹水就叻，網上大碌鳩，現實就好撚賓周"},{"pid":"094090b5930fe923c8ed1de1e40dc19b27948059","tid":762602,"uid":133680,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6974998f27c7c5eafc8ce146f94f0d3c11b4eeda","tid":762602,"uid":2748,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T14:22:03.000Z","msg":"呢D偽獨派吹水就叻，網上大碌鳩，現實就好撚賓周"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/000038_aef57e852cc46f9b2603e812e6146482.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F000038_aef57e852cc46f9b2603e812e6146482.gif&h=d21853c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6921fce84b3f0518187c0f351b0ed28cc5207395","tid":762602,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T00:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre